NAME
    Class::DBI::ViewLoader::Pg - Class::DBI::Viewloader implementation for
    Postgresql.

SYNOPSIS
    See Class::DBI::ViewLoader

DESCRIPTION
    This is the postgresql driver for Class::DBI::ViewLoader,

METHODS
  base_class
    Causes generated classes to inherit from Class::DBI::Pg.

  get_views
    See Class::DBI::ViewLoader for a description of this method.

  get_view_cols
    See Class::DBI::ViewLoader for a description of this method.

SEE ALSO
    Class::DBI::ViewLoader, Class::DBI::Loader, Class::DBI,
    <http://www.postgresql.org/>

